== 获得荣誉 ==
欧美知名游戏门户GameSpot在2006年4月12日公布了“史上最伟大游戏”票选结果，由BioWare于2000年推出的里程碑式RPG《博德之门II：安姆的阴影》以其对整个游戏界作出的持续性贡献得到了这一殊荣。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-greatest-games-of-all-time-baldurs-gate-ii-shadows-of-amn/1100-6146695/ |title=GameSpot: The Greatest Games of All Time |access-date=2015-01-07 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206205948/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-greatest-games-of-all-time-baldurs-gate-ii-shadows-of-amn/1100-6146695/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://games.qq.com/a/20090109/000154.htm |title=腾讯网：GAMESPOT 票选历史上最伟大游戏 |access-date=2015-01-07 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207085904/https://games.qq.com/a/20090109/000154.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 参考文献 ==
''Baldur's Gate 2 Game Manual''，随游戏光盘赠送。

